            <div id="review_6348549_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3621103">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3621103/" class="title-link">关键词：反思</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3621103"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/barrybai/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4720517-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/barrybai/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">白锐</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-31"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-31 15:51:11</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3621103_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  从他人反观自己，从历史反思现实，从人性反思组织，如果在读这本书时要获得什么深刻的体验，这三条维度即是标尺。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3621103/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
